SELECT assistants_clients.client_name, billing_info.billing_amount FROM assistants_clients INNER JOIN billing_info ON assistants_clients.assistant_id = billing_info.assistant_id WHERE billing_info.payment_status = 'Paid' ORDER BY billing_info.billing_amount DESC;

SELECT virtual_assistants.name, subscriptions.start_date FROM virtual_assistants INNER JOIN subscriptions ON virtual_assistants.id = subscriptions.assistant_id WHERE subscriptions.end_date < '2022-12-31' ORDER BY virtual_assistants.name ASC;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT assistant_id) AS total_assistants FROM assistants_clients WHERE subscription_id IN (SELECT subscription_id FROM subscriptions WHERE end_date > '2022-06-30');

SELECT virtual_assistants.name, subscriptions.start_date, billing_info.billing_amount FROM virtual_assistants JOIN subscriptions ON virtual_assistants.id = subscriptions.assistant_id JOIN billing_info ON subscriptions.assistant_id = billing_info.assistant_id WHERE billing_info.payment_status = 'Pending' ORDER BY billing_info.billing_amount ASC;
